<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>New Event Published</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>🎉 New Event Published!</h1>

<h2>{{ event.name }}</h2>

<p><strong>Description:</strong> {{ event.description }}</p>
<p><strong>Venue:</strong> {{ event.venue }}</p>
<p><strong>Date:</strong> {{ event.eventDate|date('F j, Y \\a\\t g:i A') }}</p>
<p><strong>Max Tickets:</strong> {{ event.maxTickets }}</p>

<p>Don't miss out - get your tickets now!</p>

<hr>
<p><small>This is an automated email from EventHub.</small></p>
</body>
</html>